#### Authorizations

HTTPBasicHTTPBearerHTTPBasicHTTPBearer

​

Authorization

string

header

required

Basic authentication header of the form `Basic <encoded-value>`, where `<encoded-value>` is the base64-encoded string `username:password`.

#### Path Parameters

​

entity

string

required

​

project

string

required

#### Query Parameters

​

evaluation_run_id

string | null

Filter by evaluation run ID

​

limit

integer | null

Maximum number of predictions to return

​

offset

integer | null

Number of predictions to skip

#### Response

Stream of data in JSONL format

​

prediction_id

string

required

The prediction ID

​

model

string

required

The model reference (weave:// URI)

​

inputs

Inputs · object

required

The inputs to the prediction

​

output

any

required

The output of the prediction

​

evaluation_run_id

string | null

Evaluation run ID if this prediction is linked to one

​

wb_user_id

string | null

Do not set directly. Server will automatically populate this field.

